    "description": "<div><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\">This month Chris, Brian and Ruthie rank their favorite Disneyland attractions, share some of their favorite Walt Disney quotes and discuss a favorite extinct attraction \"Adventure Thru Inner Space.\" They then close out the show by sharing some of their \"Disney Doin's,\" including Ruthie's Disney book collection, Brian's Disney album collection and Chris's on-line Disneyland audio collection. <br /></span></div><div><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\"><br /></span></div><div><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\">Visit our on-line store for exclusive Jiminy Crickets and DisneyChris Website Merch!!!! </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTQ3b1AwVzFKTE16N2dNamlpU2lhZjJzaldXQXxBQ3Jtc0tsOUhCMnQxaXQ1dlJmQlhHUGVqMHBnTVFDcVp2dWlMQWxGMXRvMjdaLVduTDJKTVRFTFp4Z25vbkQ0ZHdkaTZQSm1Ra3h1X2JHQWotUzRfcDU3aGZlWkd5Z0tZZ3VVTzFGNGF0NEQwa3FjTEZGeHR4MA&q=https%3A%2F%2Fjcpodcast.threadless.com%2F%E2%80%8B&v=oyrJZGHJAkU\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://jcpodcast.threadless.com/\u200b</a><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\"> <br /></span></div><div><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\"><br /></span></div><div><span class=\"style-scope yt-formatted-string\">If you would like to help support the Jiminy Crickets podcasts and DisneyChris.com - Please consider becoming a Patreon Subscriber and receive exclusive rewards every month. </span><a class=\"yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description&redir_token=QUFFLUhqbWFDb2ZtSzhEZEJyaENYZFBHR1oyX3d1MHphQXxBQ3Jtc0ttT0EtTnFMLWtGWXVZNW9GZkVCNDVfcjBOOW80dUNCZEhtYVllN3NMelhsM08yalowVGw2bXhSNmhCWFAxNmt3NHBKYTJkdEJvbWliZjhhbDY3V3NmM0NpaE5jeTdLek9xdU9uN21DRTlhN285M2lMQQ&q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2FDisneyChris&v=oyrJZGHJAkU\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.pa